&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Communicate and promote current events, product launches, and store promotions to drive traffic and increase sales.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
