&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;We are seeking an experienced, analytically driven, and strategically minded &lt;strong&gt;Wholesale Planner&lt;/strong&gt; to lead demand planning and inventory optimization across our wholesale channels. Reporting to the &lt;strong&gt;Director of Planning&lt;/strong&gt;, this role owns seasonal sales forecasting, open-to-buy management, and account-level planning. You will partner closely with Wholesale, Planning, and Finance teams to align strategies with company-wide financial goals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate is a detail-oriented, solution-oriented strategic thinker with a proven track record of driving results through data-driven decision-making in the wholesale specialty retail space.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Planning &amp;amp; Forecasting&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop seasonal and annual wholesale sales, margin, and inventory plans by channel and account.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own in-season sales forecasts, open-to-buy (OTB), and inventory flow plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generate 6, 12, and 18-month demand forecasts to ensure appropriate inventory levels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage replenishment and basics programs for both sell-in and sell-out.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the Sales team to understand customer demand and adjust merchandise plans accordingly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Inventory &amp;amp; Account Management&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain account-level demand plans and buy quantities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own pre-market buy plans, seasonal investments, and post-market reconciliation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify risks and opportunities related to inventory imbalances and implement mitigation strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support inventory optimization, stock transfers, and liquidation strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage off-price inventory and partner with Ops and Wholesale for delivery to off-price accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Analysis &amp;amp; Collaboration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze complex sales and inventory data to identify trends, product growth opportunities, and improved forecasting accuracy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with cross-functional teams to optimize supply chain processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate regularly with internal stakeholders to ensure alignment on business goals and targets.&lt;/li&gt;
